                    <br>
                    Participants may choose any of the 17 problems found here. 

                </li>

                <li><strong>Submission Round 2 - Designated Problem
                </strong>
                    <br>
                    Participants shortlisted for the second round will be given a problem by the Evaluation Board from one of the 17 problems. 
                </li>

